- <topic 1>
- <topic 2>
- <topic 3>
- <topic 4>
- <topic 5>

## Banned signals

Skip these even if engagement looks high:
- Generic motivational / hustle posts
- AI-slop posts (long em-dashed reflective threads from anonymous accounts)
- Crypto / financial advice (unless that's your niche)
- Non-English (unless your audience is multilingual)
- Posts > 14 days old (lose freshness)
